        RAM : Memory
|---------------------------|
|          Heap             | ← Dynamic Memory
|  - Objects                |    (e.g., new, malloc)
|  - Arrays (dynamic)       |
|  - Anything manually      |
|    allocated at runtime   |
|    (grows upwards ↑)      |
|---------------------------|
|          Stack            | ← Function calls & local vars
|  - Function frames        |    (grows downwards ↓)
|  - Local variables        |
|  - Pointers               |
|  - Return addresses       |
|---------------------------|
|   Static / Global Data    | ← Predefined variables
|  - Global variables       |
|  - Static variables       |
|---------------------------|
|  Source Code / Text       | ← Program instructions (read-only)
|  - Binary code            |
|  - Functions              |
|---------------------------|
